[{"text": "It's Monday morning.", "start": 15.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "In Washington,", "start": 18.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the president of the United States", "start": 20.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is sitting in the Oval Office,", "start": 22.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "assessing whether or not", "start": 24.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to strike Al Qaeda", "start": 26.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in Yemen.", "start": 28.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "At Number 10 Downing Street,", "start": 30.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "David Cameron is trying to work out", "start": 32.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "whether to cut more public sector jobs", "start": 35.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in order to stave off a double-dip recession.", "start": 38.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "In Madrid, Maria Gonzalez", "start": 41.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "is standing at the door,", "start": 44.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "listening to her baby crying and crying,", "start": 46.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "trying to work out whether she should let it cry", "start": 49.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "until it falls asleep", "start": 52.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or pick it up and hold it.", "start": 54.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And I am sitting by my father's bedside in hospital,", "start": 57.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "trying to work out", "start": 61.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "whether I should let him drink", "start": 63.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the one-and-a-half-liter bottle of water", "start": 65.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that his doctors just came in and said,", "start": 68.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "\"You must make him drink today,\" --", "start": 71.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "my father's been nil by mouth for a week --", "start": 73.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "or whether, by giving him this bottle,", "start": 76.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "I might actually kill him.", "start": 80.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We face momentous decisions", "start": 83.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with important consequences", "start": 86.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "throughout our lives,", "start": 88.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and we have strategies for dealing with these decisions.", "start": 90.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We talk things over with our friends,", "start": 93.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we scour the Internet,", "start": 96.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we search through books.", "start": 99.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But still,", "start": 102.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "even in this age", "start": 104.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of Google and TripAdvisor", "start": 106.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and Amazon Recommends,", "start": 108.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "it's still experts", "start": 111.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we rely upon most --", "start": 113.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "especially when the stakes are high", "start": 116.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the decision really matters.", "start": 118.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Because in a world of data deluge", "start": 121.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and extreme complexity,", "start": 123.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we believe that experts", "start": 126.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "are more able to process information than we can --", "start": 128.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that they are able to come to better conclusions", "start": 131.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "than we could come to on our own.", "start": 134.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And in an age", "start": 137.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that is sometimes nowadays frightening", "start": 139.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "or confusing,", "start": 142.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we feel reassured", "start": 144.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "by the almost parental-like authority", "start": 146.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of experts", "start": 149.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who tell us so clearly what it is", "start": 151.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we can and cannot do.", "start": 154.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But I believe", "start": 158.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that this is a big problem,", "start": 160.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a problem with potentially dangerous consequences", "start": 162.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "for us as a society,", "start": 166.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as a culture", "start": 169.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and as individuals.", "start": 171.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It's not that experts", "start": 173.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "have not massively contributed to the world --", "start": 175.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of course they have.", "start": 177.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "The problem lies with us:", "start": 179.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we've become addicted to experts.", "start": 182.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We've become addicted to their certainty,", "start": 185.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "their assuredness,", "start": 188.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "their definitiveness,", "start": 190.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and in the process,", "start": 192.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we have ceded our responsibility,", "start": 194.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "substituting our intellect", "start": 196.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and our intelligence", "start": 198.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "for their supposed words of wisdom.", "start": 201.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We've surrendered our power,", "start": 204.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "trading off our discomfort", "start": 207.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with uncertainty", "start": 209.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for the illusion of certainty", "start": 211.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that they provide.", "start": 213.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This is no exaggeration.", "start": 216.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "In a recent experiment,", "start": 219.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a group of adults", "start": 221.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "had their brains scanned in an MRI machine", "start": 223.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as they were listening to experts speak.", "start": 226.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The results were quite extraordinary.", "start": 230.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "As they listened to the experts' voices,", "start": 233.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the independent decision-making parts of their brains", "start": 236.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "switched off.", "start": 241.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It literally flat-lined.", "start": 243.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And they listened to whatever the experts said", "start": 246.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and took their advice, however right or wrong.", "start": 248.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But experts do get things wrong.", "start": 252.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Did you know that studies show", "start": 256.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that doctors misdiagnose", "start": 259.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "four times out of 10?", "start": 262.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Did you know", "start": 265.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that if you file your tax returns yourself,", "start": 267.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "you're statistically more likely", "start": 270.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to be filing them correctly", "start": 272.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "than if you get a tax adviser", "start": 274.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to do it for you?", "start": 276.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And then there's, of course, the example", "start": 278.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we're all too aware of:", "start": 280.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "financial experts", "start": 282.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "getting it so wrong", "start": 284.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we're living through the worst recession", "start": 286.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "since the 1930s.", "start": 288.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "For the sake of our health,", "start": 292.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "our wealth", "start": 294.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and our collective security,", "start": 296.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it's imperative that we keep", "start": 298.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the independent decision-making parts of our brains", "start": 301.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "switched on.", "start": 305.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And I'm saying this as an economist", "start": 307.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who, over the past few years,", "start": 309.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "has focused my research", "start": 311.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "on what it is we think", "start": 313.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and who it is we trust and why,", "start": 315.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but also --", "start": 318.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I'm aware of the irony here --", "start": 320.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as an expert myself,", "start": 322.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as a professor,", "start": 325.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as somebody who advises prime ministers,", "start": 327.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "heads of big companies,", "start": 330.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "international organizations,", "start": 332.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but an expert who believes", "start": 334.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that the role of experts needs to change,", "start": 336.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that we need to become more open-minded,", "start": 339.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "more democratic", "start": 342.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and be more open", "start": 344.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to people rebelling against", "start": 346.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "our points of view.", "start": 348.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So in order to help you understand", "start": 351.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "where I'm coming from,", "start": 354.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "let me bring you into my world,", "start": 356.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the world of experts.", "start": 359.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Now there are, of course, exceptions,", "start": 361.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "wonderful, civilization-enhancing exceptions.", "start": 365.26, "duration": 6.0}, {"text": "But what my research has shown me", "start": 371.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "is that experts tend on the whole", "start": 374.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to form very rigid camps,", "start": 377.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that within these camps,", "start": 380.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a dominant perspective emerges", "start": 382.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that often silences opposition,", "start": 385.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that experts move with the prevailing winds,", "start": 388.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "often hero-worshipping", "start": 391.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "their own gurus.", "start": 394.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Alan Greenspan's proclamations", "start": 396.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that the years of economic growth", "start": 398.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "would go on and on,", "start": 401.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "not challenged by his peers,", "start": 404.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "until after the crisis, of course.", "start": 407.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You see,", "start": 411.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we also learn", "start": 414.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that experts are located,", "start": 416.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "are governed,", "start": 418.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "by the social and cultural norms", "start": 420.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of their times --", "start": 423.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "whether it be the doctors", "start": 425.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in Victorian England, say,", "start": 427.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who sent women to asylums", "start": 429.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "for expressing sexual desire,", "start": 432.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "or the psychiatrists in the United States", "start": 435.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "who, up until 1973,", "start": 438.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "were still categorizing homosexuality", "start": 441.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "as a mental illness.", "start": 445.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And what all this means", "start": 447.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is that paradigms", "start": 449.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "take far too long to shift,", "start": 451.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that complexity and nuance are ignored", "start": 454.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "and also that money talks --", "start": 458.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "because we've all seen the evidence", "start": 461.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of pharmaceutical companies", "start": 464.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "funding studies of drugs", "start": 466.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that conveniently leave out", "start": 469.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "their worst side effects,", "start": 471.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "or studies funded by food companies", "start": 474.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of their new products,", "start": 477.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "massively exaggerating the health benefits", "start": 480.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of the products they're about to bring by market.", "start": 483.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The study showed that food companies exaggerated", "start": 486.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "typically seven times more", "start": 488.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "than an independent study.", "start": 491.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And we've also got to be aware", "start": 495.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that experts, of course,", "start": 497.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "also make mistakes.", "start": 499.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "They make mistakes every single day --", "start": 501.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "mistakes born out of carelessness.", "start": 504.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "A recent study in the Archives of Surgery", "start": 507.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "reported surgeons", "start": 510.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "removing healthy ovaries,", "start": 512.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "operating on the wrong side of the brain,", "start": 515.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "carrying out procedures on the wrong hand,", "start": 518.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "elbow, eye, foot,", "start": 521.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and also mistakes born out of thinking errors.", "start": 524.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "A common thinking error", "start": 527.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of radiologists, for example --", "start": 529.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "when they look at CT scans --", "start": 532.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "is that they're overly influenced", "start": 535.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "by whatever it is", "start": 537.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that the referring physician has said", "start": 539.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that he suspects", "start": 541.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the patient's problem to be.", "start": 543.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So if a radiologist", "start": 546.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is looking at the scan", "start": 548.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of a patient with suspected pneumonia, say,", "start": 550.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "what happens is that,", "start": 553.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "if they see evidence", "start": 555.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of pneumonia on the scan,", "start": 557.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "they literally stop looking at it --", "start": 560.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "thereby missing the tumor", "start": 563.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "sitting three inches below", "start": 565.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "on the patient's lungs.", "start": 567.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I've shared with you so far", "start": 571.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "some insights into the world of experts.", "start": 574.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "These are, of course,", "start": 577.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "not the only insights I could share,", "start": 579.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but I hope they give you a clear sense at least", "start": 581.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of why we need to stop kowtowing to them,", "start": 584.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "why we need to rebel", "start": 587.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and why we need to switch", "start": 589.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "our independent decision-making capabilities on.", "start": 591.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "But how can we do this?", "start": 595.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Well for the sake of time,", "start": 598.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I want to focus on just three strategies.", "start": 601.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "First, we've got to be ready and willing", "start": 606.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to take experts on", "start": 608.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and dispense with this notion of them", "start": 611.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as modern-day apostles.", "start": 614.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This doesn't mean having to get a Ph.D.", "start": 616.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in every single subject,", "start": 619.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you'll be relieved to hear.", "start": 621.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But it does mean persisting", "start": 623.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in the face of their inevitable annoyance", "start": 626.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "when, for example,", "start": 629.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we want them to explain things to us", "start": 631.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in language that we can actually understand.", "start": 633.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Why was it that, when I had an operation,", "start": 638.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "my doctor said to me,", "start": 641.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"Beware, Ms. Hertz,", "start": 643.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of hyperpyrexia,\"", "start": 645.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "when he could have just as easily said,", "start": 647.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"Watch out for a high fever.\"", "start": 649.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You see, being ready to take experts on", "start": 653.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "is about also being willing", "start": 657.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to dig behind their graphs,", "start": 659.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "their equations, their forecasts,", "start": 662.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "their prophecies,", "start": 664.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and being armed with the questions to do that --", "start": 666.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "questions like:", "start": 669.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "What are the assumptions that underpin this?", "start": 671.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "What is the evidence upon which this is based?", "start": 674.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "What has your investigation focused on?", "start": 677.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "And what has it ignored?", "start": 681.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It recently came out", "start": 684.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that experts trialing drugs", "start": 686.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "before they come to market", "start": 689.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "typically trial drugs", "start": 691.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "first, primarily on male animals", "start": 694.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "and then, primarily on men.", "start": 698.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It seems that they've somehow overlooked the fact", "start": 701.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that over half the world's population are women.", "start": 704.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And women have drawn the short medical straw", "start": 709.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "because it now turns out that many of these drugs", "start": 712.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "don't work nearly as well on women", "start": 715.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as they do on men --", "start": 718.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the drugs that do work well work so well", "start": 720.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that they're actively harmful for women to take.", "start": 723.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Being a rebel is about recognizing", "start": 726.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that experts' assumptions", "start": 729.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and their methodologies", "start": 732.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "can easily be flawed.", "start": 734.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Second,", "start": 737.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we need to create the space", "start": 739.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "for what I call \"managed dissent.\"", "start": 742.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "If we are to shift paradigms,", "start": 745.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "if we are to make breakthroughs,", "start": 747.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "if we are to destroy myths,", "start": 749.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we need to create an environment", "start": 752.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in which expert ideas are battling it out,", "start": 754.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in which we're bringing in", "start": 757.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "new, diverse, discordant, heretical views", "start": 759.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "into the discussion,", "start": 762.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "fearlessly,", "start": 764.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in the knowledge that progress comes about,", "start": 766.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "not only from the creation of ideas,", "start": 769.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "but also from their destruction --", "start": 773.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and also from the knowledge", "start": 776.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that, by surrounding ourselves", "start": 779.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "by divergent, discordant,", "start": 781.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "heretical views.", "start": 784.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "All the research now shows us", "start": 786.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that this actually makes us smarter.", "start": 788.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Encouraging dissent is a rebellious notion", "start": 793.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "because it goes against our very instincts,", "start": 796.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "which are to surround ourselves", "start": 799.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with opinions and advice", "start": 802.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we already believe", "start": 804.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "or want to be true.", "start": 807.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And that's why I talk about the need", "start": 809.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to actively manage dissent.", "start": 811.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Google CEO Eric Schmidt", "start": 815.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is a practical practitioner", "start": 817.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of this philosophy.", "start": 820.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "In meetings, he looks out for the person in the room --", "start": 822.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "arms crossed, looking a bit bemused --", "start": 825.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and draws them into the discussion,", "start": 828.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "trying to see if they indeed are", "start": 831.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the person with a different opinion,", "start": 834.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "so that they have dissent within the room.", "start": 837.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Managing dissent", "start": 840.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is about recognizing the value", "start": 842.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of disagreement, discord", "start": 845.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and difference.", "start": 848.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But we need to go even further.", "start": 850.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We need to fundamentally redefine", "start": 853.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "who it is that experts are.", "start": 856.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The conventional notion", "start": 860.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is that experts are people", "start": 862.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with advanced degrees,", "start": 865.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "fancy titles, diplomas,", "start": 867.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "best-selling books --", "start": 870.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "high-status individuals.", "start": 872.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But just imagine", "start": 874.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "if we were to junk", "start": 876.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "this notion of expertise", "start": 878.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "as some sort of elite cadre", "start": 882.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "and instead embrace the notion", "start": 886.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of democratized expertise --", "start": 889.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "whereby expertise was not just the preserve", "start": 892.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of surgeons and CEO's,", "start": 895.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but also shop-girls -- yeah.", "start": 897.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Best Buy,", "start": 901.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the consumer electronics company,", "start": 903.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "gets all its employees --", "start": 905.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the cleaners, the shop assistants,", "start": 908.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the people in the back office,", "start": 910.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "not just its forecasting team --", "start": 913.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to place bets, yes bets,", "start": 915.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "on things like whether or not", "start": 918.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a product is going to sell well before Christmas,", "start": 920.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "on whether customers' new ideas", "start": 923.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are going to be or should be taken on by the company,", "start": 926.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "on whether a project", "start": 930.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "will come in on time.", "start": 932.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "By leveraging", "start": 934.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and by embracing", "start": 936.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the expertise within the company,", "start": 938.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Best Buy was able to discover, for example,", "start": 940.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that the store that it was going to open in China --", "start": 943.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "its big, grand store --", "start": 947.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "was not going to open on time.", "start": 949.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Because when it asked its staff,", "start": 952.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "all its staff, to place their bets", "start": 954.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "on whether they thought the store would open on time or not,", "start": 957.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "a group from the finance department", "start": 961.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "placed all their chips", "start": 964.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "on that not happening.", "start": 966.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It turned out that they were aware,", "start": 969.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as no one else within the company was,", "start": 971.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of a technological blip", "start": 974.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that neither the forecasting experts,", "start": 976.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "nor the experts on the ground in China,", "start": 978.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "were even aware of.", "start": 981.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The strategies", "start": 985.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that I have discussed this evening --", "start": 987.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "embracing dissent,", "start": 990.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "taking experts on,", "start": 992.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "democratizing expertise,", "start": 994.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "rebellious strategies --", "start": 996.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are strategies that I think", "start": 999.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "would serve us all well to embrace", "start": 1001.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as we try to deal with the challenges", "start": 1003.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of these very confusing, complex,", "start": 1006.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "difficult times.", "start": 1009.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "For if we keep", "start": 1011.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "our independent decision-making part", "start": 1013.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of our brains switched on,", "start": 1015.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "if we challenge experts, if we're skeptical,", "start": 1018.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "if we devolve authority,", "start": 1021.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "if we are rebellious,", "start": 1023.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but also", "start": 1025.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "if we become much more comfortable", "start": 1027.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with nuance,", "start": 1029.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "uncertainty and doubt,", "start": 1031.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and if we allow our experts", "start": 1034.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to express themselves", "start": 1037.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "using those terms too,", "start": 1039.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we will set ourselves up", "start": 1041.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "much better", "start": 1043.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for the challenges of the 21st century.", "start": 1045.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "For now, more than ever,", "start": 1049.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "is not the time", "start": 1052.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to be blindly following,", "start": 1054.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "blindly accepting,", "start": 1056.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "blindly trusting.", "start": 1058.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now is the time to face the world", "start": 1061.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with eyes wide open --", "start": 1064.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "yes, using experts", "start": 1067.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to help us figure things out, for sure --", "start": 1069.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I don't want to completely do myself out of a job here --", "start": 1072.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "but being aware", "start": 1076.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of their limitations", "start": 1078.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and, of course, also our own.", "start": 1081.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 1085.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 1087.26, "duration": 5.0}]